---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About cappuccino.io — what it is, why it exists, and who writes it."
>
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-22 pb-28">

    <header class="mb-16">
      <p class="small-caps font-body text-caption text-espresso/45 tracking-widest mb-6">
        About
      </p>
      <h1 class="font-display text-h2 text-ink max-w-[18ch]">
        A site about cappuccino.
      </h1>
    </header>

    <div class="max-w-[65ch] space-y-6">

      <p class="font-body text-body text-espresso leading-[1.75]">
        Cappuccino.io is a topical authority site focused entirely on one drink.
        Not espresso generally, not the café industry, not coffee as lifestyle —
        the cappuccino. Its components, its technique, its equipment, and its
        variations.
      </p>

      <p class="font-body text-body text-espresso leading-[1.75]">
        The site exists because the cappuccino is a specific drink with specific
        requirements, and most of the writing about it is either too vague to be
        useful or too precious to be honest. The goal here is accuracy.
      </p>

      <p class="font-body text-body text-espresso leading-[1.75]">
        Articles are written by Sara Vitale. Product recommendations contain
        affiliate links, which are disclosed on every page that has them.
        Brands listed on the{' '}
        <a
          href="/brands"
          class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-espresso/30 hover:text-ink transition-colors duration-150"
        >
          Brands page
        </a>{' '}
        pay for placement. Editorial content — reviews, guides, technique — is
        independent of the sponsorship directory.
      </p>

      <p class="font-body text-body text-espresso leading-[1.75]">
        Questions or corrections: write to{' '}
        <a
          href="mailto:contact@cappuccino.io"
          class="underline underline-offset-4 decoration-espresso/30 hover:text-ink transition-colors duration-150"
        >
          contact@cappuccino.io
        </a>.
      </p>

    </div>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
